title: Anti-military protests in Myanmar on anniversary of 1988 uprising - Reuters
description: Protests against Myanmar's military government broke out across the nation on Sunday, the anniversary of the bloody suppression of a 1988 uprising against a previous army junta.

title: Taliban capture government buildings in Afghan city of Kunduz - Reuters
description: Taliban fighters have seized key government buildings in the northeastern Afghan city of Kunduz, leaving government forces hanging onto control of the airport and their own base, a provincial assembly lawmaker said on Sunday.
